data.description: Great two story home with formal dining room, large Great Room with french door to covered lanai and backyard. Spacious kitchen with breakfast area, loads of cabinets and breakfast bar. Huge master suite with his and her walk in closets. Master bath with garden tub and separate shower. Roomy loft which could have many uses; including game room or additional family room.  Thanks!
